00:00:25.160 --> 00:00:28.130
TO HANDLING NEGATIVE COMMENTS TO MEDITATIONS

00:00:28.130 --> 00:00:31.440
FOR PREVENTING A FREAK-OUT MOMENT.

00:00:31.440 --> 00:00:34.970
