00:00:34.970 --> 00:00:36.780
GABRIELLE BERNSTEIN.

00:00:36.780 --> 00:00:46.450
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

00:00:46.450 --> 00:00:50.320
NEW YEAR'S DAY OF 2015,

00:00:50.320 --> 00:00:53.390
I HAD A PLAN.

00:00:53.390 --> 00:00:55.860
MY PLAN WAS TO GET PREGNANT.

00:00:55.860 --> 00:00:57.190
I HAD IT DOWN. IT WAS PERFECT.

00:00:57.190 --> 00:00:59.900
I WAS GONNA GET PREGNANT RIGHT AWAY, IN FEBRUARY,

00:00:59.900 --> 00:01:02.900
I WAS GONNA TAKE THE ENTIRE NINE MONTHS TO WRITE MY BOOK,

00:01:02.900 --> 00:01:04.340
"THE UNIVERSE HAS YOUR BACK,"

00:01:04.340 --> 00:01:06.610
AND I WAS GONNA GIVE BIRTH IN THE FALL,

00:01:06.610 --> 00:01:08.970
AND THEN HAVE THE BABY, GIVE BIRTH, SUBMIT THE BOOK,

00:01:08.970 --> 00:01:11.410
THEN TAKE THREE MONTHS OFF WITH MY BABY,

00:01:11.410 --> 00:01:12.880
AND GO ON A BOOK TOUR.

00:01:12.880 --> 00:01:14.750
PERFECT PLAN, RIGHT?

00:01:14.750 --> 00:01:16.980
PERFECT PLAN.

00:01:16.980 --> 00:01:21.650
THE ONLY PROBLEM WAS -- I WASN'T GETTING PREGNANT.

00:01:21.650 --> 00:01:23.650
MONTH AFTER MONTH, I WOULDN'T GET PREGNANT,

00:01:23.650 --> 00:01:25.990
AND I'D START COUNTING NINE MONTHS AHEAD.

00:01:25.990 --> 00:01:28.030
I'D START LOOKING AT WHAT I HAD AHEAD OF ME.

00:01:28.030 --> 00:01:31.000
I'D START THINKING, "OKAY, I'VE GOT THIS SPEAKING ENGAGEMENT.

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:32.760
I'VE GOT THIS CONTRACT I'VE GOT TO DEAL WITH."

00:01:32.760 --> 00:01:35.000
AND I STARTED CANCELING THOSE CONTRACTS AND CANCELING

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:36.770
THOSE SPEAKING ENGAGEMENTS.

00:01:36.770 --> 00:01:38.700
I STARTED DRIVING MY PUBLISHERS CRAZY,

00:01:38.700 --> 00:01:39.900
BECAUSE I WAS TRYING TO CHANGE

00:01:39.900 --> 00:01:42.010
THE PUBLICATION DATE OF THE BOOK.

00:01:42.010 --> 00:01:43.640
I WAS DRIVING MY HUSBAND CRAZY,

00:01:43.640 --> 00:01:45.940
BECAUSE THERE'S ABSOLUTELY NOTHING SEXY ABOUT

00:01:45.940 --> 00:01:50.550
TRYING TO MAKE A BABY HAPPEN ON YOUR TIMELINE.

00:01:50.550 --> 00:01:51.950
AND I'M DRIVING MYSELF CRAZY,

00:01:51.950 --> 00:01:53.620
BECAUSE I'M TRYING TO CONTROL SOMETHING

00:01:53.620 --> 00:01:56.490
THAT I ABSOLUTELY CANNOT CONTROL.

00:01:56.490 --> 00:01:59.260
BUT ALL THE WHILE, I'M TELLING MY FRIENDS AND FAMILY MEMBERS

00:01:59.260 --> 00:02:02.690
THAT I'M CONSCIOUSLY CONCEIVING.

00:02:02.690 --> 00:02:07.130
I WAS CONSCIOUSLY CONTROLLING EVERY DETAIL.

00:02:07.130 --> 00:02:11.840
AND SIX MONTHS GO BY, AND I'M STILL NOT PREGNANT.

00:02:11.840 --> 00:02:13.740
AT THIS POINT, I START TO WORRY.

00:02:13.740 --> 00:02:15.440
"I'M GETTING OLDER.

00:02:15.440 --> 00:02:17.780
MY BODY ISN'T WORKING.

00:02:17.780 --> 00:02:19.580
THERE'S SOMETHING WRONG WITH ME."

00:02:19.580 --> 00:02:22.580
I START TO FEEL THIS SENSE OF SHAME,

00:02:22.580 --> 00:02:24.420
BUT I'M NOT GONNA TALK ABOUT IT.

00:02:24.420 --> 00:02:26.990
I'M NOT TELLING ANYBODY HOW I'M FEELING.

00:02:26.990 --> 00:02:29.020
EVERY TIME I GO ON INSTAGRAM OR FACEBOOK,

00:02:29.020 --> 00:02:31.520
