00:02:31.520 --> 00:02:35.160
AND I FEEL SEPARATE AND I FEEL ALONE

00:02:35.160 --> 00:02:39.430
AND I BEGIN TO COMPARE MYSELF TO EVERYONE AROUND ME.

00:02:39.430 --> 00:02:40.570
TO MAKE MATTERS WORSE,

00:02:40.570 --> 00:02:42.670
I HAD PREMATURELY ANNOUNCED MY PREGNANCY

00:02:42.670 --> 00:02:44.540
TO MY FRIENDS AND MY FAMILY MEMBERS.

00:02:44.540 --> 00:02:47.370
I EVEN WENT AS FAR AS TO GET ON MY STAGES, PUBLICLY,

00:02:47.370 --> 00:02:49.070
AND TELL MY STUDENTS

00:02:49.070 --> 00:02:51.280
THAT I WAS PLANNING TO CONCEIVE.

00:02:51.280 --> 00:02:52.480
AND THIS GOT REALLY BAD.

00:02:52.480 --> 00:02:54.310
IT GOT SO BAD THAT I WAS AT A BOOK SIGNING,

00:02:54.310 --> 00:02:55.610
AND THIS YOUNG WOMAN GRABS MY HAND

00:02:55.610 --> 00:02:58.080
