00:02:58.080 --> 00:03:00.390
AND SHE SAYS, "YOU KNOW, GABBY,

00:03:00.390 --> 00:03:02.790
I'VE BEEN CHANNELING YOUR SPIRIT BABY,

00:03:02.790 --> 00:03:07.860
AND SHE HAS A MESSAGE FOR YOU."

00:03:07.860 --> 00:03:12.030
THIS REALLY PUSHED ME OVER THE EDGE.

00:03:12.030 --> 00:03:14.200
SIX MORE MONTHS GO BY.

00:03:14.200 --> 00:03:17.940
IT'S NEW YEAR'S EVE.

00:03:17.940 --> 00:03:20.370
I'M AT A DINNER WITH ALL OF MY COLLEGE FRIENDS,

00:03:20.370 --> 00:03:22.710
AND THEY ALL HAVE AT LEAST ONE CHILD,

00:03:22.710 --> 00:03:24.380
MAYBE A SECOND ON THE WAY.

00:03:24.380 --> 00:03:27.010
ANOTHER COUPLE HAD ADOPTED A CHILD.

00:03:27.010 --> 00:03:28.950
AND I'M SITTING AROUND THIS DINNER TABLE

00:03:28.950 --> 00:03:31.420
AND I'M LOOKING AT EVERYBODY PREPARE THEIR KIDS FOR DINNER

00:03:31.420 --> 00:03:33.120
AND GET THEM READY FOR BED

00:03:33.120 --> 00:03:36.890
AND I'M FEELING LIKE I'M BEHIND.

00:03:36.890 --> 00:03:39.960
I'M MISSING OUT ON THIS STAGE OF LIFE

00:03:39.960 --> 00:03:44.000
AND I'M NOT FEELING GOOD ENOUGH.

00:03:44.000 --> 00:03:48.870
I WAKE UP THE NEXT DAY, NEW YEAR'S DAY,

00:03:48.870 --> 00:03:51.640
A FULL YEAR LATER,

00:03:51.640 --> 00:03:54.810
AND I GOT MY PERIOD.

00:03:54.810 --> 00:03:59.740
I SPENT A YEAR TRYING TO MAKE THIS THING HAPPEN.

00:03:59.740 --> 00:04:03.010
I SPENT A YEAR TRYING TO MAKE MY BODY DO SOMETHING

00:04:03.010 --> 00:04:05.420
THAT IT'S NOT GONNA DO.

00:04:05.420 --> 00:04:06.620
I'M FEELING THAT SHAME.

00:04:06.620 --> 00:04:08.820
I'M FEELING THAT INADEQUACY, THAT SEPARATION.

00:04:08.820 --> 00:04:12.760
I'M NOT GOOD ENOUGH. I CAN'T MAKE THIS HAPPEN.

00:04:12.760 --> 00:04:14.560
THANKFULLY, I HAD A FRIEND STAYING WITH ME,

00:04:14.560 --> 00:04:17.560
MY FRIEND JORDAN, A VERY GREAT SPIRITUAL RUNNING BUDDY OF MINE.

00:04:17.560 --> 00:04:20.160
