00:04:24.300 --> 00:04:25.800
AND I SAID, WELL, YOU KNOW, JORDAN,

00:04:25.800 --> 00:04:28.040
I COULDN'T MAKE IT HAPPEN. MY BODY ISN'T WORKING.

00:04:28.040 --> 00:04:29.810
I CAN'T MAKE IT HAPPEN ON MY TIMELINE.

00:04:29.810 --> 00:04:31.310
I TRIED TO CHANGE EVERYTHING AROUND.

00:04:31.310 --> 00:04:33.780
IT WASN'T WORKING. "HONEY, STOP.

00:04:33.780 --> 00:04:38.580
THIS IS NOT HOW WE DO THINGS.

00:04:38.580 --> 00:04:42.220
ASK THE UNIVERSE FOR HELP."

00:04:42.220 --> 00:04:45.990
